About 2 to 3 \ h% of all people on earth may have a fantasy to a

67
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:18,420
some degree, but many are not even aware that they have the condition,

68
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:22,120
So the actual figure can be higher.

69
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:27,660
We still know very little about Avantasi, but the research is ongoing.

70
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:30,560
The important thing to take with you is to aphantasi

71
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:34.560
should not be seen as an obstacle to living a full life.

72
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:39,600
Many who have the condition are not even aware of it and have successfully

73
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:43,780
learned to navigate through everyday life without the need

